      "writtenOn": "2022-01-13T17:55:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "run_env has all three of inheritable_fds, args, and env.  Can you be more specific?\n\nLooking at other variants, I will need to deal with whether cmd is path or fd, and whether inheritable_fds remaps or not.  It can be ugly to handle path/fd uniformly.  It should be fine to make inheritable_fds always remap, but it will be less convenient to use.",
