      "writtenOn": "2022-01-13T21:17:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sorry for the confusion.  What I\u0027d like to see is `fn run(\u0026self, config: RunConfig)`, instead of run {,_env} x {, _fd} x {,_remap}, which we don\u0027t currently have.  Now there\u0027s RunConfig, you\u0027d only need to move inheritable_fds into it?  You might want to consider adding an `enum InheritableFds`, something along the line with:\n\n enum InheritableFds {\n   Keep(Vec\u003cRawFd\u003e),\n   Remap(Vec\u003c(RawFd, RawFd)\u003e),\n }\n\nWDYT?",
